re common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Robert Symes was born in 1390, in Barnsley, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom, his father, John Symes, was 31 and his mother, Sarah Bentshot, was 31. He married Ruth de Barnsley in 1388, in Barnsley, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 2 sons. He died in 1433, in his hometown, at the age of 43."},"et":{"1390–1433":"1390–1433","1390–1410":"1390–1410","1408–1492":"1408–1492","1410–1492":"1410–1492","1360–1434":"1360–1434","1360–1391":"1360–1391","about 1408":"umbes 1408","1434":"1434","1433":"1433","1410":"1410","about 1389":"umbes 1389","about 1410":"umbes 1410","1360":"1360","1492":"1492","1408":"1408","1391":"1391","1390":"1390","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","Barnsley, Yorkshire, England":"Barnsley, Yorkshire, England"},"fi":{"1390–1433":"1390–1433","1390–1410":"1390–1410","1408–1492":"1408–1492","1410–1492":"1410–1492","1360–1434":"1360–1434","1360–1391":"1360–1391","about 1408":"noin 1408","1434":"1434","1433":"1433","1410":"1410","about 1389":"noin 1389","about 1410":"noin 1410","1360":"1360","1492":"1492","1408":"1408","1391":"1391","1390":"1390","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","Barnsley, Yorkshire, England":"Barnsley, Yorkshire, England"},"fr":{"1390–1433":"1390–1433","1390–1410":"1390–1410","1408–1492":"1408–1492","1410–1492":"1410–1492","1360–1434":"1360–1434","1360–1391":"1360–1391","about 1408":"environ 1408","1434":"1434","1433":"1433","1410":"1410","about 1389":"environ 1389","about 1410":"environ 1410","1360":"1360","1492":"1492","1408":"1408","1391":"1391","1390":"1390","Yorkshire, England":"Everwyck, Angleterre","Barnsley, Yorkshire, England":"Barnsley, Everwyck, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Robert Symes est né en 1390, à Barnsley, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, John Symes, avait 31 ans et sa mère, Sarah Bentshot, avait 31 ans. Il a épousé Ruth de Bar